title: Kamaru Usman emeriela Jorge Masvidal n’ọkpọ UFC
sentences: Nwaafọ Naịjirịa bụ Kamaru Usman eturula ugo ọzọ n’asọmpi ọkpọ a kpọrọ Welterweight UFC
O ji ọkpọ kurichaa Jorge Masvidal eze oge ha abụ zutere n’ụtụtụ ụbọchi Sọnde
Masvidal mara Usman aka ịnapụ ya mgbanukwu ya mana Usman gosiri ya ihe ọkụ ji ntị oke eme
